data.description: Welcome to 3718 Snow Fawn Avenue, a stunning 5-bedroom, 5-bathroom house that offers the perfect blend of style and comfort. This spacious property spans over 3360 square feet, giving you plenty of room to create memories with your loved ones. The well-appointed bedrooms provide ample space for relaxation and privacy, while the guest quarters or casita present an opportunity for multi-generational living or a home office setup. Located in a gated community.  This home is just minutes away from parks, schools, and all the amenities you need. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity!
